{"Bat Fact":"Lakuriq\u00ebt e nat\u00ebs vampir\u00eb si un\u00eb jo vet\u00ebm q\u00eb fluturojm\u00eb, por ne ecim, k\u00ebrcejm\u00eb dhe vrapojm\u00eb n\u00eb tok\u00eb.","Black Cat Fact":"Ndryshe nga macet e tjera t\u00eb m\u00ebdha, ne jaguar\u00ebve na p\u00eblqen t\u00eb notojm\u00eb dhe t\u00eb kalojm\u00eb koh\u00eb n\u00eb uj\u00eb.","End Screen":"G\u00ebzuar Hallouinin! (dhe mos harro t\u00eb lash dh\u00ebmb\u00ebt!)","Happy Halloween!":"G\u00ebzuar Hallouinin!","Octopus Fact":"Un\u00eb kam tri zemra! Vet\u00ebm dy pompojn\u00eb kur notoj, k\u00ebshtu q\u00eb preferoj t\u00eb zvarritem.","Option":"B\u00ebj zgjedhjen t\u00ebnde!","Owl Fact":"Puplat n\u00eb k\u00ebmb\u00ebt e mia m\u00eb mbajn\u00eb ngroht\u00eb si pantofla me push.","Spider Fact":"Ne tarantulat e heqim skeletin ton\u00eb t\u00eb jasht\u00ebm plot me qime p\u00ebr t'u rritur, ashtu si merimangat e tjera.","Treat":"Karamele","Trick":"Rreng","Trick or Treat?":"Rreng apo karamele?","Wolf Fact":"Ul\u00ebrima \u00ebsht\u00eb thjesht nj\u00eb m\u00ebnyr\u00eb se si ne ujq\u00ebrit komunikojm\u00eb. Ne jemi ekspert\u00eb t\u00eb gjuh\u00ebs s\u00eb trupit dhe shprehjeve t\u00eb fytyr\u00ebs."}